snippet.title: REI: a girl with wings Trailer
snippet.description:
[REI: a girl with wings] is coming to 2024.
REI is a gliding action adventure game inspired by 『ICO』 and 『Portal』. Become a small but brave boy in a ruined world and fly while holding the hand of a winged girl. Jump through space and time with the necklace. Uncover the secrets of the abandoned laboratory and escape.
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2846150/REI_a_girl_with_wings/
